{"tid":1077550,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"飯係食物界嚟講都幾犀利","createTime":"2019-03-25T15:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T01:30:13.000Z","uid":198607,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e1e3370fd670441a6a5b2048002400b7e3417c","tid":1077550,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"雖然唔食飯係可以食烏冬米線米粉公仔麵油麵幼麵拉麵通粉 甚至係麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但以上 要你搵一款一日三餐都食 食足一個月 就算幾好食 就算日日配唔同嘅野嚟食 都會厭 (雖然試過全日不斷食麵包 但日日食嘅話 身為麵包撚都厭同有少少反胃)<br />\n<br />\n但係飯就唔同 唔同嘅餸就唔同味覺衝擊 就算無餸 齋食白飯都可以食成碗 無胃口個陣 撈水撈茶都好好食 一日三餐都完全唔會厭 佢自己又好多花款 可以變粥可以變壽司 特別啲變炒米又得 想健康啲又變紅米飯 基本上可以食死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7099b79b2627fd467285f23b0ee8f8b4592c0ea","tid":1077550,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"我老豆成日話食咗幾十年飯食嫌晒 成日都淨係食餸"},{"pid":"e0380d4875af38dc42b333b446560ccfa8a47c85","tid":1077550,"uid":198607,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"d7099b79b2627fd467285f23b0ee8f8b4592c0ea","tid":1077550,"uid":71657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"我老豆成日話食咗幾十年飯食嫌晒 成日都淨係食餸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:01:15.000Z","msg":"竟然會有人食厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d03d0179936fa66c27202a0d1a9101531a19be1","tid":1077550,"uid":64374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b20befa2e03d9cba01633a86cdf94c824d1fee84","tid":1077550,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4d03d0179936fa66c27202a0d1a9101531a19be1","tid":1077550,"uid":64374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T